metadata.name: Kaia
metadata.description: I fall asleep after a long insomnia.  Nightmares attack me and want to hunt me down.  I am full of fear and anxiety.  But always among these fears, a girl appears who protects me.  She brings a world full of color and peace and protects me from nightmares.  She is my dream.  A dream that is opposed to a nightmare. Her name is Kaia and she is there to kill the Boogeyman.
